{"tid":853002,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"再岀名嘅米芝連餐廳都超越唔到佢","createTime":"2018-10-08T09:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T11:04:46.000Z","uid":60171,"like":11,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"242bfad507a77ce362c64b5f1a88521e5d92afed","tid":853002,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"阿爸阿媽煮嘅每一餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時雖然係普普通通嘅飯餸<br />\n但嗰種味道你係喺岀面餐廳點食都食唔岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其係阿媽煲嘅湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡簡單單一碗粟米蘿蔔湯都可以飲落好甜，唔止係味蕾上嘅滿足，仲滿足埋心靈<br />\n<br />\n人大左就會發現愈來愈少時間同屋企人食飯，可能因為返工要加班，可能因為約左朋友，可能因為已經搬左岀去住.........<br />\n見面嘅時間變得愈嚟愈少<br />\n<br />\n就算係咁，佢地都依然咁愛錫你，仲會擔心你喺岀面食夠唔夠飽，岀街有無著夠衫，有無小心過馬路<br />\n<br />\n望住你一日一日咁長大，由起初一個生得幾條頭髮嘅豆丁，依家已經岀嚟投身社會<br />\n<br />\n日子一日一日咁過，當你再坐低同爸爸媽媽食飯嘅時候，你會發現佢地不自不覺多左皺紋，白頭髮都愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n原來佢地都慢慢變老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚，你會唔會返屋企食晚飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8550637779c3603bfbca3e7a096e03edd5385eed","tid":853002,"uid":16956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"雞翼魚蛋湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5247259e36d1792b51fc2e74b0494b45886091c","tid":853002,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"邊個俾負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff31f867c9f0902469c085c15cac7fb047e7051","tid":853002,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"要OT, 不了"},{"pid":"8c1f1af3735638979e6e8f91aa93cfb160ae9fb4","tid":853002,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"過馬路小心d啊你！"},{"pid":"a1d8758f7ba2b00426d47af65a2249d83f351898","tid":853002,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"0.5<br />\n太嬌情做作"}]}